ng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%91%C3%A0o/poem-7RF7hWSSvMz9Brg4SD1kgA">Hải đào - 海濤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/author-GaA0SgEPvCmkAgLupJfzCQ">Trần Bích San</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%ADt-m%E1%BB%99-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-l%E1%BA%A1c-phong-di%E1%BB%87c-kh%E1%BB%9Fi/poem-rRYSphjANe-zNN-I1GaBaA">Nhật mộ (Nhật lạc phong diệc khởi) - 日暮（日落風亦起）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%C3%A1i-th%E1%BB%A9-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-V3Zx1DLOhzjjBq07BnLIew">Tái thứ nguyên vận - 再次原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/Thanh-b%C3%ACnh-nh%E1%BA%A1c/poem-aFAsVoScd8WMBLwsuOsCdg">Thanh bình nhạc - 清平樂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-d%E1%BB%AF-Ho%C3%A0ng-Giang-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-ph%C3%BA/poem-F37ZvPfrMpMsTIpYAEUL2g">Thu dạ dữ Hoàng Giang Nguyễn Nhược Thuỷ đồng phú - 秋夜與黃江阮若水同賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-Lan-T%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Vu-trung-h%E1%BA%A3o-Thu%E1%BB%B3-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-%C3%82m-S%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0nh-l%E1%BB%99-nan/poem-lPwjbRD8q6kpZYIDAjYzIw">Vu trung hảo (Thuỳ đạo Âm Sơn hành lộ nan) - 于中好（誰道陰山行路難）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-Lan-T%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-4UIcOQq3X5B-YNUldGF_5g">Nạp Lan Tính Đức</